sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as AI Agent<br/>(Claude Desktop/Code)
    participant MCP as RHOAI MCP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MR as Model Registry<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant NN as Neural Navigator<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Git as Git Repository<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Helm as Helm/oc CLI<br/>(subprocess)

    Note over Agent,K8s: Flow 1: AI Agent Tool Execution (e.g. list_workbenches)
    Agent->>MCP: MCP Request (stdio/SSE/HTTP)<br/>tool: list_workbenches
    MCP->>K8s: GET /apis/kubeflow.org/v1/notebooks<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    K8s-->>MCP: Notebook list (JSON)
    MCP-->>Agent: MCP Response<br/>formatted results + _source metadata

    Note over Agent,MR: Flow 2: Model Registry Query
    Agent->>MCP: MCP Request<br/>tool: list_registered_models
    MCP->>K8s: GET ModelRegistry CR<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    K8s-->>MCP: Registry namespace & service info
    MCP->>MR: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>HTTP | None (in-cluster)
    MR-->>MCP: Registered models JSON
    MCP-->>Agent: MCP Response<br/>model list with benchmarks

    Note over Agent,NN: Flow 3: Neural Navigator Recommendation
    Agent->>MCP: MCP Request<br/>tool: recommend_model
    MCP->>NN: POST /api/v1/extract<br/>HTTP | None
    NN-->>MCP: Deployment intent extraction
    MCP->>NN: POST /api/v1/ranked-recommend-from-spec<br/>HTTP | None
    NN-->>MCP: Ranked model recommendations<br/>(GPU-aware, SLO-based)
    MCP-->>Agent: MCP Response<br/>ranked recommendations

    Note over Agent,Helm: Flow 4: Quickstart Deployment
    Agent->>MCP: MCP Request<br/>tool: deploy_quickstart
    MCP->>Git: git clone<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    Git-->>MCP: Repository contents
    MCP->>Helm: helm install / oc apply<br/>(subprocess)
    Helm->>K8s: Create resources<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    K8s-->>Helm: Resource created
    Helm-->>MCP: Deployment result
    MCP-->>Agent: MCP Response<br/>deployment status
